name: FitScrypt
description: FitScrypt is revolutionizing the crypto space for the better. The mass adoption of crypto is taking place at this very moment. FitScrypt allows you to earn crypto while keeping yourself healthy and introducing you to the transition from Web 2.0 to Web 3.0. FitScrypt is a community driven project that launched on the Binance Smart Chain. Under leadership of a doxed development team, FitScrypt will set standards in transparency and offer true utility.
